The paper discusses the evaluation of research paper recommendation systems, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL) in the recommendation system. Additionally, the paper focuses on the evaluation of a literature recommendation platform (cs.DL) and the collection of user click data (cs.CY).
